overview: Bob's printer isn't working, but that's because it's not plugged in. Zac shows Bob a little something about plugging.  Val needs a favor from his co-worker David. To help him figure out why his penis hurts. Val's gonna love David's help.  David's working late, checking out some secret files. Denis catches him, and the two get down to some secrets of their own.  Joey's hungry so he orders a pizza to the office, but he realizes he's hungrier for the pizza boy, Thor.  Matthew is the new guy, and Nicolas wants to make him feel good on his first day of work.
title: Office Twinks 4
